{"tid":1511257,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日職工盟改左去中環集會","createTime":"2019-08-27T13:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T13:37:59.000Z","uid":23949,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8fa81216c83b5b7886eb421fd25524ca6cfdc723","tid":1511257,"uid":23949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:06:58.000Z","msg":"消息來源：李卓仁facebook<br />\n<br />\n今日職工盟上訴警方禁制工會在國泰城集會，最後被駁回。依家緊急轉變集會地點下午四時去愛丁堡廣場，遊行去太古廣場向太古總部抗議。整個上訴過程，律政司代表主要都係話係因為禁制令禁制任何集會，同埋不斷假設如果有事發生就會影響機場運作。仲講埋國泰反對，因為國泰認為集會影響國泰城內嘅運作。當然我哋覺得如果國泰咁緊張自己嘅運作同埋形象，就應該唔好解僱。解僱得又唔敢面對員工。另外以律政司代表嘅邏輯，任何集會都假設會出事，咁其實全香港乜嘢地方都唔使集會。不過香港市民都已經去到母畏母懼嘅地步，大家繼續抗爭，五大訴求缺一不可。<br />\n#撤回解僱決定<br />\n#停止白色恐怖"},{"pid":"26326333720e69893435440168678e4401150cc5","tid":1511257,"uid":56227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:08:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3GVOQD0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3GVOQD0.jpg&h=8464bc81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"017be69e4822413991c2466bcd7d9142b081327c","tid":1511257,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:08:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80117ad43166c27dab8a88b3b68a24aba2e0dcf","tid":1511257,"uid":2612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h89LSSA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh89LSSA.gif&h=778b9ffb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e23c31909ff7b30b4a36337ea961e2b61bd28c60","tid":1511257,"uid":23949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:10:32.000Z","msg":"828中環 國泰 metoo集會<br />\n831<br />\n91機場見"},{"pid":"8c468b7c0d8a3a972df9b10386d28a44e020cd22","tid":1511257,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d80117ad43166c27dab8a88b3b68a24aba2e0dcf","tid":1